{"tid":947861,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"點解我老豆要咁狠心？","createTime":"2018-12-19T15:00:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T16:04:35.000Z","uid":202317,"like":9,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"fa7c97406f75e10275fe9c365c03bc1c96cf9427","tid":947861,"uid":202317,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:00:25.000Z","msg":"由3歲開始 就已經有二奶<br />\n18年黎都無睇過我一眼。<br />\n唔會比家用 反而知我有返part time 問返我借錢<br />\n人人都話佢出面有養二奶 全屋人都唔信佢<br />\n得我一個信老豆<br />\n次次都借錢比佢 <br />\n結果呢？<br />\n比我兜口兜面見到佢拖住個二奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n喊到痞左係地下到 結果佢都只係同我講<br />\n企返係身喇 好多人望住呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n點解要利用我對你嘅信任呀？<br />\n我真係好想死<br />\nSorry for 1999<br />\n有無人可以鼓勵下我 真係真係好辛苦..."},{"pid":"4a19d14aa5346740ea0af4757cc69fd6cd72f9d1","tid":947861,"uid":810,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:00:52.000Z","msg":"你只係副產物"},{"pid":"1580b64f3b96f898b37563416d27ae9ff5b4a51b","tid":947861,"uid":185022,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:01:59.000Z","msg":"努力活下去,搶走佢二奶"},{"pid":"44a2582eb249a784ae3213e70640458fe27a4833","tid":947861,"uid":102179,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:03:13.000Z","msg":"全家人都唔信剩係信老豆就抵撚死啦<br />\n你老母見到你信老豆都唔信佢仲傷心呀"},{"pid":"cf70e058d4a86c368b8bd075f69e97abea025d8b","tid":947861,"uid":14497,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:12:09.000Z","msg":"弱智仔"},{"pid":"623840bae30ddd031ac37b879bda5d78d35aa9e8","tid":947861,"uid":82175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:13:40.000Z","msg":"你老豆又唔係你"},{"pid":"f12009d3457d5783778c17200224aa84aff2a70e","tid":947861,"uid":88029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T15:14:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d58cc569cc3b75558bf8c40420623631571b86b3","tid":947861,"uid":185374,"like